Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.55,0:50:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.55,0:50:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.55,0:50:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.55,0:50:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.55,0:50:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.78,0:50:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.78,0:50:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.78,0:50:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dentist. He's been a dentist practicing for 10 years, and his observation is that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.86,0:50:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,people have bad habits like clenching your teeth and those things. These bad habits exert
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.51,0:50:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,certain forces through your oral muscles, and then his guess is that leads to all the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.42,0:51:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,oral problems. He wants to know whether, through kinesiology, he wants to know whether that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.69,0:51:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.50,0:51:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure about the question. People form nervous habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.00,0:51:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by clenching their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.78,0:51:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose clenching teeth is a way to diverge.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.05,0:51:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But anger, irritation, and he may be correct that by doing that, they do eventually pay
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.80,0:51:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain price. Yes, I think it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.28,0:51:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Clenching their teeth all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.28,0:51:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.38,0:51:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.38,0:51:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If his observation is correct, he wants to know, confirm that through kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.57,0:51:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so he could say, confirm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.59,0:51:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether those bad habits leads to oral problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.09,0:51:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oral diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.09,0:51:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.09,0:51:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.09,0:51:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.09,0:52:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.09,0:52:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And another question. He's doing Course in Miracle all by himself, without teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.69,0:52:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any sort of dangers that he should be aware of?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.61,0:52:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.61,0:52:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, doing alone, doing it all by himself, without teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.61,0:52:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.61,0:52:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Any danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.61,0:52:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.61,0:52:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing you can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.76,0:52:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.76,0:52:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not dangerous to forgive people.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.76,0:52:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.76,0:52:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I forgot one more question for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.76,0:52:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.76,0:52:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He then, he told his patients, stop doing that bad habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.09,0:52:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And patients do not listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.09,0:52:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.09,0:52:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wants to know how, how can he make his patients stop those bad habits more effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.09,0:52:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they do it without even, it's in their subconscious, because they don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.09,0:52:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.09,0:52:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.09,0:52:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.09,0:52:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.09,0:52:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.09,0:52:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.09,0:52:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.09,0:52:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.09,0:52:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.09,0:52:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.09,0:52:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.09,0:52:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.09,0:52:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.09,0:52:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.09,0:52:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.09,0:52:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.09,0:52:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.09,0:52:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.09,0:52:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.09,0:52:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.09,0:52:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.09,0:53:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He tells them no, because they do some clutching the teeth is sometimes done
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.09,0:53:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sleep form, and you do it subconsciously rather than even consciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.80,0:53:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.78,0:53:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to retrain the patient, and use hypnosis perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.88,0:53:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and because there are a lot of cases of doing something goatie just like that has
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.34,0:53:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,been difficult, you need to re-educate the patient, to examinez the patient, and do some
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.75,0:53:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,will help you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.26,0:53:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep cleansing during the day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.01,0:53:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's almost all you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.50,0:53:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do that almost all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.40,0:53:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to fix it after you recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.80,0:53:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.73,0:53:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad habits are good for your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.84,0:53:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.88,0:53:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.00,0:54:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.19,0:54:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.01,0:54:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the true state of knowingness the same as the state of absolute love?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.13,0:54:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those two the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.42,0:54:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different states.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.90,0:54:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.94,0:54:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different styles of trying to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.94,0:54:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.03,0:55:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, knowingness on the level that he's asking this is very much the field in which this love occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.48,0:55:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Agape.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.00,0:55:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That type of love is called agape.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.48,0:55:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impersonal way of being in the world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.84,0:55:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The two are the same, and they are two different ways of expressing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.34,0:55:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The state of the question you are asking is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.23,0:55:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, the two levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.78,0:55:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The condition is that the level of love you get from this type of love, which is called agape.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.17,0:55:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're talking about love as the quality of your personality in terms of your personality in this world and What character are you speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.61,0:55:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.67,0:55:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.05,0:55:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,�
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.30,0:55:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.15,0:56:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some unconscious patterns of bad behavior is repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.80,0:56:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it happens so fast, like an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.76,0:56:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In an instant, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.40,0:56:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So it feels like an irremovable mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.38,0:56:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I overcome this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.15,0:56:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.84,0:56:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're conquered.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.80,0:56:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.42,0:56:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.80,0:56:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.48,0:56:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Plead with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.55,0:57:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.17,0:57:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.67,0:57:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is exactly what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.92,0:57:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of behavior are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.78,0:57:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, in a couple's relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.90,0:57:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when they fight, they keep fighting in the same pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.42,0:57:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep fighting with the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.01,0:57:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a complaint about my wife's insecurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.51,0:57:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife has a complaint about my lack of self-esteem and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.96,0:57:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a complaint about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.40,0:57:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if we keep fighting with different topics,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.17,0:57:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the focus keeps repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, the fight, I mean, they have a fight with his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.42,0:57:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He fights, but over the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.34,0:58:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She complains about the fact that he's not generous enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.32,0:58:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.86,0:58:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's not satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.19,0:58:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That she is always sort of agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.65,0:58:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.96,0:58:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever the subject is, it ends up always with the same complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.13,0:58:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So this pattern is repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.88,0:58:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it, yeah, that's his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.71,0:58:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.63,0:58:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.57,0:58:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.11,0:58:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.63,0:58:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay on the floor and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.86,0:58:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.46,0:58:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.71,0:58:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.17,0:58:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.98,0:58:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.65,0:58:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.90,0:58:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry, cry, cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.92,0:58:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.25,0:58:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.51,0:59:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And because this way she's trying to change him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.23,0:59:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way she's trying to get her way in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.21,0:59:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.09,0:59:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.63,0:59:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby cries and cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.09,0:59:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And makes things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.59,0:59:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She better grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.98,0:59:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And accept how the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.09,0:59:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop being eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.63,0:59:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.98,0:59:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.03,0:59:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.30,0:59:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.76,1:00:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that isn't even tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.65,1:00:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a minor problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.23,1:00:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what tough is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.05,1:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it doesn't create agony or, you know, something severe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.01,1:00:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you're always blubbering and crying instead of, you know, cutting the potatoes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.11,1:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.19,1:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You get tears in the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.26,1:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You get tears in the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.48,1:00:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.44,1:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, see, within each one, there is the adult, the child, and the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.90,1:00:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a good pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.90,1:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Within everybody, there is the child, the adolescent, the adult, and the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.03,1:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These sort of archetypes are in everybody's personality, and you give too much energy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.92,1:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to the child, you give too much energy to the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.86,1:01:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In you is also the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.96,1:01:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say to the parent in you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.90,1:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In you is also the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.90,1:01:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say to the parent in you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.05,1:01:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the child to stop that and grow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.51,1:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the child to stop that and grow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.09,1:01:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is greater happiness, greater happiness to be found when you let go of being childish.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.46,1:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is greater happiness, greater happiness to be found when you let go of being childish.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.80,1:02:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You then experience the happiness of the adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.09,1:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so indulging the child within you, you cheat your adult of the satisfaction of being
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.21,1:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a well-functioning, respectable adult, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.26,1:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So by indulging the child in her, she's cheating the adult in her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.71,1:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to ask herself how she can help him be a better person, to make herself happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.55,1:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So is she saying he's stingy?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.96,1:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.59,1:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stingy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.50,1:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not generous and kind enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.05,1:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.17,1:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionally, not money-wise.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.65,1:03:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.61,1:03:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And she needs to know that's how he is and accept that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.15,1:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.65,1:03:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he will feel free to share his emotions with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.00,1:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.28,1:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another story.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.96,1:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another style of therapy called psychodrama.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.88,1:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychodrama.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.59,1:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychodrama.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.07,1:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It might also be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.71,1:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he think about what she says?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.63,1:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he think?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.57,1:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's not saying anything.
