Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.65,1:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.65,1:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she saw a person sitting next to her and she knew that it was a person from her past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.65,1:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.65,1:14:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.65,1:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a Buddhist monk.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.77,1:15:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And she then came a thought asking, which one is me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.90,1:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This person or that person?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.90,1:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the answer said, only consciousness is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.73,1:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a very sharp, almost screaming voice said, what am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.03,1:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And intuitively she knew that this voice will dominate my life from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.14,1:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.17,1:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And second experience happened at age seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.17,1:15:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At age seven or eight on a spring day.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.57,1:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And she felt a sunshine on her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.10,1:15:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And she knew that she was entering the world of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.96,1:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And from then on, she knew intuitively all the Buddhist teachings because she was probably a Buddhist in her past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.40,1:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is this non-verbal knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.65,1:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal knowingness that the universe itself is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.23,1:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And she saw how petty human love is compared to that infinite love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.52,1:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the world is a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.52,1:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When a flower blooms, she sees a smile there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.52,1:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she said, then question came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.97,1:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she thought I came here just after I passed the level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.97,1:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And why am I not living as an enlightened person?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.97,1:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And her understanding is, I experienced enlightenment but a mind attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.97,1:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.28,1:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.28,1:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she was, she thought that she passed the level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.96,1:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.96,1:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then her question was.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.96,1:17:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.07,1:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She did transcend level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.50,1:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.50,1:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then her question is, why am I not living?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.01,1:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As an enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.01,1:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she not leaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.01,1:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's enlightenment got to do with leaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.01,1:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.01,1:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.01,1:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Living a life.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.01,1:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Living a life as an enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.01,1:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.01,1:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then her answer was, to my enlightened state, a mind was attached.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.35,1:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.02,1:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced union mystica with a mind attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.85,1:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.85,1:17:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still of mind, not of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.10,1:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still of mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.38,1:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So her mind was stronger than her spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.38,1:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, her mind's controlling.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.18,1:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She identifies her reality as the mind instead of spirit?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.18,1:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.50,1:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.50,1:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.50,1:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of why she's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.50,1:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bad understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.50,1:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.50,1:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The third experience happened at age 13.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.50,1:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.50,1:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two words, positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.50,1:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And she forgot all about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.61,1:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And she spent her past 50 years experiencing the whole gamut of emotions below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.61,1:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,From 20 to 175.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.61,1:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.61,1:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she did 12 steps group for eight years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.61,1:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Through that, she regained the memory of those three experiences, profound experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.61,1:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question she's asking is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.61,1:18:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she really wants that all her struggle throughout 50 years, spiritual struggle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.93,1:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really want that to come to a spiritual fruition.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.18,1:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is not able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.18,1:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.18,1:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she mean by fruition?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.39,1:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.28,1:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's still going through emotions below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.28,1:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.28,1:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then she wasn't over 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.28,1:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She could have been in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in a past life she.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.28,1:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Might have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.35,1:19:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.84,1:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask where she's at now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.84,1:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's over 200, 400, 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.52,1:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's trying to figure things out in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.22,1:19:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.68,1:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's trying to understand intellectually in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.81,1:19:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She should stop trying to understand it intellectually.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.81,1:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter what she thinks, it's going to be nonsense anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.89,1:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to figure it out intellectually.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.89,1:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to manipulate your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.90,1:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.81,1:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much self-consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.81,1:20:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be and stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.81,1:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she also said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.81,1:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.81,1:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She understood that those experiences inflated her spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.81,1:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she thinks now that is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.81,1:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost she's feeling humility now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.81,1:20:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.81,1:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.81,1:20:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So then asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.81,1:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,These experiences, these profound experiences inflated her spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.81,1:21:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.81,1:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.81,1:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.81,1:21:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.81,1:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Got inflated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.81,1:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Made something out of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.94,1:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.94,1:21:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.94,1:21:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it stopped doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.94,1:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.94,1:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.94,1:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels of those experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.94,1:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.94,1:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What experiences?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.94,1:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The three profound experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.94,1:21:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The three experiences she had.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.94,1:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.61,1:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.61,1:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.81,1:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.81,1:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the first experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.81,1:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the light she saw at four.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.81,1:21:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The light she saw at age four.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.81,1:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.81,1:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was over 600, 700, 650.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.85,1:21:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.85,1:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.85,1:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The next experience was.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.77,1:21:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.77,1:21:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.77,1:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In which she got the understanding that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.06,1:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Entire universe itself is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.06,1:21:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.53,1:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that calibrated over 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.69,1:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,750.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.96,1:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,About 700, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.96,1:22:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.96,1:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's number two.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.22,1:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's number three?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.22,1:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.22,1:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.22,1:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.22,1:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.22,1:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.22,1:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.22,1:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.22,1:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three was what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.22,1:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.22,1:22:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.22,1:22:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.46,1:22:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaningless to me, out of context.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.42,1:22:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have to look at the context.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.47,1:22:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have to look at the context.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.67,1:23:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she has the power to write down all the spiritual experiences she underwent throughout her life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.10,1:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she has the power to write that down.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.10,1:23:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Write it down for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.10,1:23:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For others to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.10,1:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.18,1:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that could be helpful to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.18,1:24:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it helpful?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.18,1:24:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what it means, so what's the message she's going to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.18,1:24:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.68,1:24:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.93,1:24:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.43,1:24:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.43,1:24:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Without thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.43,1:24:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's ruminating.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.27,1:24:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's ruminating, thinking, judging, processing it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.27,1:24:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.34,1:24:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I make a song.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.34,1:24:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I go, la la la la la la la la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.34,1:24:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.22,1:24:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I say, that was a good song, that was a bad song, that was a famous song.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.89,1:25:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a rerun of a song from a childhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.89,1:25:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a song that signifies the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.89,1:25:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a song from the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.89,1:25:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a song.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.89,1:25:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all spinning with the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.89,1:25:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.89,1:25:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,La la la la la la la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.89,1:25:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.89,1:25:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a song like this, that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.21,1:25:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you hear this song?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.21,1:25:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of song is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.21,1:25:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.21,1:25:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.21,1:25:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.68,1:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,La la la la la la la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.68,1:25:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.68,1:25:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.68,1:25:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.68,1:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.68,1:25:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.68,1:25:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.68,1:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.68,1:25:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.68,1:25:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.68,1:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.68,1:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.42,1:25:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.42,1:25:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.42,1:25:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.67,1:25:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.67,1:25:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.67,1:25:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.67,1:25:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.02,1:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom, bap, bap, boom, bap, boom, boom, boom, boom, boom, boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.56,1:25:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.27,1:25:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting speed, just to let them be.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.46,1:25:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.46,1:26:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them be.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.98,1:26:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.53,1:26:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll directly ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.34,1:26:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.34,1:26:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She speaks English.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.34,1:26:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.39,1:26:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.39,1:26:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um ... It seems like this one is experiencing constant accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.60,1:26:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,conflict at home so and i've been um praying as you said praying um as god's help and um knowledge
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.48,1:26:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowledge for god's will and power to carry that out and also uh as for miracle and uh
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.30,1:26:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly trying to uh see it differently and all those things for a couple of years now
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.50,1:27:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stressful like how it's more like i'm creating and experiencing more uh conflict with my spouse
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.26,1:27:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,oh your spouse yes yes and the basic uh basic thing
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.77,1:27:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that i'm trying to make sure that i'm not the only one who's having a hard time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.92,1:27:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and i'm trying to make sure that i'm not the only one who's having a hard time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.93,1:27:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is more like there's a huge differences
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.34,1:27:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,between our belief system,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.76,1:27:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and his belief system is there's no life after death,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.76,1:27:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.14,1:27:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.97,1:27:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I'm coming here almost 10 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.52,1:27:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, constantly, and every time,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.43,1:27:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's a lot of,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.26,1:27:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this one is creating lots of conflict at home
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.47,1:27:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that, and I've been praying,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.88,1:27:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to create any more bad karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.56,1:27:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could see his viewpoint, and I understand,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.65,1:27:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could feel his pain, and I cannot agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.81,1:27:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his pain, what pain?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.18,1:27:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't believe in God, so what's his pain about?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.30,1:27:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His pain is that you are a believer in God?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.18,1:27:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.18,1:27:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His pain is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.31,1:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.43,1:28:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you keep it to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.63,1:28:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in God, I don't care if anybody else agrees with me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.22,1:28:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or knows about it, I don't make a,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.71,1:28:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't stand up and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.81,1:28:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a believer in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.97,1:28:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want us to all believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.64,1:28:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my private inner self.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.72,1:28:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that create conflict?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.92,1:28:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he doesn't want me to go away and really,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.73,1:28:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.06,1:28:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away where?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.14,1:28:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.97,1:28:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.81,1:28:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.65,1:28:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritual practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.50,1:28:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.34,1:28:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying to prevent him from.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.34,1:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.18,1:28:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing her religious beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.23,1:28:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, so you tell him,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.34,1:28:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to accept your atheism,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.96,1:28:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, in return, you must accept my theism.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.69,1:28:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't like it,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.14,1:28:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then you must live with somebody else, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.30,1:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.53,1:28:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.38,1:28:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm praying for, what is the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.14,1:28:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, either should I stay with this guy or no?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.61,1:28:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm praying for a couple of years now,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.07,1:28:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't get any answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.22,1:28:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.96,1:28:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.27,1:29:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.11,1:29:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, and I believe that, but it's.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.96,1:29:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the answer you're getting is to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.47,1:29:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.94,1:29:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Patience.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.23,1:29:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.07,1:29:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.89,1:29:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.73,1:29:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They both have to have tolerance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.57,1:29:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.44,1:29:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerance for each other's wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.89,1:29:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.73,1:29:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.57,1:29:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to control him,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.00,1:29:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes, it feels like he's,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.96,1:29:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like he's a better human being than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.02,1:29:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's a very respectable guy in some way,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.85,1:29:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's very responsible, and I respect that,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.03,1:29:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe I, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.60,1:29:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.85,1:29:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.63,1:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I cannot, anything I could do,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.75,1:30:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but this, I cannot give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.47,1:30:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is my, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.86,1:30:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.93,1:30:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's, but it seems like it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.43,1:30:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the conflict is getting worse, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.11,1:30:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, answer yourself and you pray, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.39,1:31:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he should not stop you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.14,1:31:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, he can stop me, but he's getting angry,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.09,1:31:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and creating a lot of conflict at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.67,1:31:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he can't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.09,1:31:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he can.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.77,1:31:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.67,1:31:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, but he's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.34,1:31:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.94,1:31:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.23,1:31:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a question in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.15,1:31:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard, but you're inner.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.53,1:31:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you can show him your spiritual belief, he will accept.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.46,1:31:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very common for the man to be the businessman, logical, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.68,1:31:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the woman goes to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.85,1:32:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very common.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.03,1:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman and the children go to church, and he figures, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.31,1:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's for women and children.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.65,1:32:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because his mind is on business and logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.72,1:32:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the different archetypes that the male and female come from sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.55,1:32:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, do you think you could calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.47,1:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the highest good that I'm leaving him?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.52,1:32:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest good that you should leave him?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.43,1:32:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.42,1:32:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Make God happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.92,1:32:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that too, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.69,1:32:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.77,1:32:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really calibrate a decision like that, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.89,1:32:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the best way is I keep praying.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.89,1:32:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to show him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.02,1:32:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to agree?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.43,1:32:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why they have to agree about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.36,1:32:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to understand the culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.57,1:33:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A Korean man can stop a woman from doing anything they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.73,1:33:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.43,1:33:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a culture thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.88,1:33:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't stopping her, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.47,1:33:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.18,1:33:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.69,1:33:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's allowing her to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.47,1:33:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the solution is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.00,1:33:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.60,1:33:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.02,1:33:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer to it is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.31,1:33:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love him enough to accept the way he is and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.44,1:33:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to cross over is with love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.97,1:33:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him the love in you as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.17,1:33:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.02,1:33:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The compromise is via love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.39,1:33:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, you can't solve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.02,1:33:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.10,1:33:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So love will either solve it or it won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.81,1:33:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there's not enough love, then you won't solve it because there isn't enough love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.10,1:33:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If love is more important than anything else, then you'll stay with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.39,1:34:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If other things are more important, then that will dissolve the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.92,1:34:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on what you want from a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.81,1:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't find love in a relationship, goodbye relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.72,1:34:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what's a relationship all about?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.42,1:34:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about love.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.43,1:34:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there isn't love, then there's no reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.92,1:34:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.57,1:34:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.53,1:34:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.64,1:34:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.25,1:34:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.09,1:34:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.55,1:34:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.98,1:34:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.35,1:34:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.90,1:34:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Send him over.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.72,1:34:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.52,1:34:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.97,1:34:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I try.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.17,1:34:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have a last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.86,1:34:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.59,1:34:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.98,1:34:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.73,1:34:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take a break either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.68,1:34:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.44,1:34:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.89,1:34:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.55,1:34:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have to go to the bathroom too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.64,1:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody may need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.14,1:34:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.75,1:34:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.52,1:35:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He has two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.14,1:35:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.43,1:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.59,1:35:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The first question is, when I was four years old, my family got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.75,1:35:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was four?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.22,1:35:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.44,1:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was four years old, entire family got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.51,1:35:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.40,1:35:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody got hurt, but only his mother died.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.68,1:35:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.13,1:35:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years later, his father got remarried, and he's got a stepmother, and then he divorced again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.36,1:35:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.61,1:35:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.02,1:35:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.18,1:35:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.34,1:35:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.39,1:35:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.53,1:36:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And after a few years after that, his father got remarried, and he's living with the second stepmother until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.53,1:36:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.31,1:36:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.02,1:36:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.84,1:36:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,26.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.61,1:36:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Through these experiences, what sort of karmic understanding he could get from this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.82,1:36:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of human life, you see, the nature of human life,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.17,1:36:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,takes many forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.25,1:36:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are various diversions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.35,1:36:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And to accept that, there are multitudinous patterns
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.69,1:36:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of which the conventional ones are only one alternative.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.65,1:37:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably more people living
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.42,1:37:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in unconventional circumstances
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.42,1:37:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,than there are in conventional circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.39,1:37:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, what, 50% of marriages end in divorce, 50%.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.47,1:37:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the norm?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.63,1:37:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The norm is to get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.82,1:37:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.97,1:37:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, many times your parents get married two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.31,1:37:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.81,1:37:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, parents get married two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.85,1:37:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, parents get married two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.02,1:37:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's really his father's karma, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.72,1:37:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, this is more related to his father's karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.64,1:38:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The second question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.44,1:38:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live with courage and dignity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.14,1:38:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to follow the teaching of the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.65,1:38:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.03,1:38:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve that, I am praying.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.89,1:38:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to live his life with dignity and courage, and he wants to devote his life to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.57,1:38:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,your teachings, and what is the best way of doing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.31,1:39:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The books all tell you how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.98,1:39:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Through prayer, meditation, and being loving towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.42,1:39:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be non-judgmental about things about which you have an aversion, but to not be
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.81,1:39:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,judgmental about things that you have aversion to.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.89,1:39:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But to not be judgmental about things that you have aversion to.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.90,1:39:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that is the way it is for those people and their karma, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.77,1:39:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.10,1:39:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean it's wrong, it just means it's not your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.43,1:39:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in blowing up busloads of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.61,1:39:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my way, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.97,1:39:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in blowing up busloads of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.44,1:39:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in blowing up buses of children, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.05,1:40:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in a和 and to one of the best ways of living, which is to not be judgmental
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.85,1:40:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,towards it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.85,1:40:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is sentient, to remain a person, not to have a roots of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.90,1:40:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the same way, to pass on to other people those who come to you with a sense of resentment,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.94,1:40:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to feelness of resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.10,1:40:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a inner strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.64,1:40:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason of not having a inner strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.07,1:40:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a inner strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.23,1:40:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.34,1:40:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still believe in positive actions?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.77,1:40:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.84,1:40:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in positive actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.10,1:40:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.30,1:40:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, do you believe in such things?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.57,1:40:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.84,1:40:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in positive actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.03,1:40:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you see how the, how is the Komodo dragon, the Komodo dragon, one bite and you're
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.52,1:40:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.78,1:40:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hate the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.35,1:40:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't put your foot in its cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.35,1:40:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can respect everything being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.52,1:40:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.56,1:41:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.93,1:41:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You accept that it's part of divine creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.36,1:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And people would say, well, why would God create a Komodo dragon?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.18,1:41:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.18,1:41:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.18,1:41:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put your foot in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.02,1:41:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see.
