Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.61,1:41:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.61,1:42:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So we need to take a short break. How do we work it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.73,1:42:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we will ask your blessings for some people.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.73,1:42:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For the people?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.73,1:42:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby and people, some people with sickness.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.73,1:42:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people want your healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.73,1:42:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.73,1:42:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After the break.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.73,1:42:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, yes. All right, so now we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.73,1:42:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.73,1:42:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.78,1:42:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.78,1:42:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.46,1:42:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have answered some of the questions more fully.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.68,1:42:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I give thanks for your being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.68,1:42:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your being here is like a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.68,1:42:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love these people here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.68,1:42:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the Korean people in general and these people here in particular.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.68,1:42:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.68,1:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.68,1:42:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless you in the name of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.10,1:42:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.10,1:43:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful people, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.60,1:43:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some blessings to do at this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.40,1:43:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.40,1:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a, if you want to turn around here, there is women that are expecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.40,1:43:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.40,1:43:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And they, I don't know if you want to sit down for this, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.30,1:43:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.30,1:43:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.30,1:43:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stand up, we'll stand up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.30,1:43:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take a, we'll get a sip of water.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.75,1:43:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Little boy who cut class to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.03,1:43:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, why are we seeing him?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.03,1:43:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again, just giving this blessing because he wanted to come and.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.03,1:43:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you and thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.03,1:43:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.57,1:43:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.57,1:43:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.57,1:43:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.57,1:43:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.57,1:43:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.57,1:43:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.57,1:43:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good week.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.57,1:43:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.57,1:44:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.57,1:44:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.57,1:44:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.57,1:44:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.06,1:44:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.06,1:44:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.92,1:44:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.92,1:44:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.92,1:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.57,1:44:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.57,1:44:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.57,1:44:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.57,1:44:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.57,1:44:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.57,1:44:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.57,1:44:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.57,1:44:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What a divine being.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.57,1:44:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.57,1:44:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A divine being.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.57,1:44:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.57,1:44:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.57,1:44:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a child of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.28,1:44:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.28,1:44:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for such a lovely child.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.39,1:44:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God created another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.89,1:44:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.56,1:44:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.06,1:44:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God created another one!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.07,1:44:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried that before with him and he didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.93,1:45:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he likes you. He loves you, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.34,1:45:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, you were created by God, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.02,1:45:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless the baby in your womb. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.22,1:45:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,God's creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.22,1:45:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All creatures are creatures of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.77,1:45:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hold within your womb the creation of God
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.00,1:45:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have reverence for it
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.42,1:45:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and reverence that you have been chosen as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.17,1:45:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.17,1:45:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't chosen by God to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.17,1:45:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were chosen by God to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.17,1:46:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, otherwise you wouldn't be pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.52,1:46:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And a great blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.61,1:46:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.61,1:46:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.61,1:46:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.61,1:46:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know the conflict between North Korea and South Korea.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.61,1:46:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.61,1:46:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.26,1:46:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's one of the men who are defending.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.26,1:46:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.18,1:46:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the army?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.43,1:46:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.43,1:46:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.43,1:46:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.43,1:46:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the army?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.43,1:46:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.43,1:46:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.09,1:46:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the Navy in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.09,1:46:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.88,1:46:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, serviceman.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.17,1:46:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Service.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.17,1:47:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Service is a great thing to experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.19,1:47:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to be part of a whole army, part of a whole ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.43,1:47:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.35,1:47:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Great experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.01,1:47:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you make friendships that last many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.31,1:47:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.31,1:47:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a small ship, 26.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.23,1:47:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,26.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.84,1:47:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the war, we sent each other cards for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.93,1:47:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.93,1:47:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.25,1:47:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.25,1:47:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.25,1:47:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For years and years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.25,1:47:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year I got Christmas cards from other crew members.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.25,1:47:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And gradually as the years went by, the number of cards got fewer and fewer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.65,1:48:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This year I got.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.11,1:48:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say none.
